          },
          {
            "text": " as the base: its mild alcohol content gives it partial preservative properties and its astringency helps reduce surface bacteria. Arrowroot powder absorbs sweat; tea tree and lavender tackle the odour-causing bacteria that cause underarm smell. This spray needs a thorough shake before each use as the arrowroot settles.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
